// The items with the inserted gems are in the other script, called
// itens_gemmed.scp, because there are pretty many of them.
// Below bgeins the Tinkering menus to insert the gems inside
// the items' sockets. This is cool because it links two different
// skills with one single purpose, and I pretty liked it this way
// although some players amde some complaints about it, but
